channel.title: Comments on: Corona Geek #185 – Spine workflow basics and using Tiled as a level editor

item.title: By: Yoozoo
item.dc:creator: Yoozoo
item.description: Fantastic podcast this week. Thanks for the many insights Michael Wilson, Tiled looks worthy of investigation. Spine does a great job at making Corona content look good for prospective new users.
